Package: libsnapmanager
Section: admin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsnapwebsites
Suggests: snapmanagercgi, snapmanagerdaemon
Description: Fast Websites: powerful CMS for Apache written in C++.
